title: Imagini șocante ale războiului din Ucraina: un rus și un ucrainean se împușcă în tranșee, de la un metru distanță/ Video
cleaned_sentences: A terrifying moment was surprised by a drone, on the battlefield in Ukraine.
Russia Today has published a video in which a Russian and a Ukrainian are seen in trenches.
While the Russians are looking for the last Ukrainian soldiers, there was a Ukrainian soldier in trenches.
The two are trapped in a battle of life and death, in which they are drawn in blindness.
At one point, the Russian soldier advances and the two get to pull from a short distance to each other.
The confrontation was won by the Russian soldier, the one who left, the Ukrainian soldier being killed with a burst of bullets.
